and had a child out of wedlock!

1028
01:02:44,594 --> 01:02:48,139
This is the thanks we get
for taking you in?

1029
01:02:49,557 --> 01:02:51,268
Goodness!

1030
01:02:51,351 --> 01:02:52,811
Same old script, I see.

1031
01:02:54,312 --> 01:02:55,939
You're laughing? Why you little…

1032
01:02:56,773 --> 01:02:58,858
Are you even guarding the building at all?

1033
01:02:58,942 --> 01:03:01,861
What's the point of having security
if you're just going to let

1034
01:03:01,945 --> 01:03:03,154
this riff-raff disrupt work?

1035
01:03:03,238 --> 01:03:05,782
What? "Riff-raff"?

1036
01:03:05,865 --> 01:03:07,033
My apologies.

1037
01:03:07,701 --> 01:03:09,244
- Drag them out.
- Yes, ma'am.

1038
01:03:09,828 --> 01:03:10,870
This way.

1039
01:03:11,579 --> 01:03:13,623
- Where is the police?
- Should I call them again?

1040
01:03:13,707 --> 01:03:15,875
Yes, report them
for obstruction of business.

1041
01:03:15,959 --> 01:03:18,753
Let go of me! I can leave on my own!

1042
01:03:21,089 --> 01:03:22,132
You want money?

1043
01:03:23,049 --> 01:03:24,467
My mom sent me to college.

1044
01:03:24,551 --> 01:03:27,178
And at most,
you paid for a year's worth of tuition.

1045
01:03:27,262 --> 01:03:28,513
"Living expenses"?

1046
01:03:29,639 --> 01:03:33,351
Shall I calculate and bill you
for 14 years of forced domestic labor

1047
01:03:33,435 --> 01:03:35,145
with five hours of sleep per day?

1048
01:03:36,688 --> 01:03:37,814
If you ever visit me again,

1049
01:03:37,897 --> 01:03:40,233
I will destroy you all.

1050
01:04:05,425 --> 01:04:07,177
- Are you okay?
- What do you mean?

1051
01:04:07,260 --> 01:04:09,596
That fight earlier with your ex-husband.

1052
01:04:09,679 --> 01:04:11,014
Why would I not be okay?

1053
01:04:11,639 --> 01:04:12,557
You were really cool.

1054
01:04:15,894 --> 01:04:17,270
- Do you have plans today?
- Why?

1055
01:04:17,354 --> 01:04:18,521
Should we have dinner?

1056
01:04:18,605 --> 01:04:19,898
I'm watching what I eat.

1057
01:04:19,981 --> 01:04:22,317
Really? Me too.
I want to lose some weight.

1058
01:04:22,400 --> 01:04:25,236
I know a good salad place nearby.
How about some salad?

1059
01:04:25,737 --> 01:04:27,197
No.

1060
01:04:27,280 --> 01:04:28,865
Then what about
that soup and rice place

1061
01:04:28,948 --> 01:04:30,825
- we used to go--
- No.

1062
01:04:36,915 --> 01:04:38,500
Why do you keep wasting time on me?

1063
01:04:38,583 --> 01:04:39,542
What?

1064
01:04:39,626 --> 01:04:42,379
Aren't you going to get married?
Do you have infinite time or something?

1065
01:04:42,462 --> 01:04:44,255
What's the point of having a meal with me?

1066
01:04:44,339 --> 01:04:47,342
Go out and date. If that doesn't work,
have someone set you up.

1067
01:04:48,510 --> 01:04:50,845
Why waste precious time eating with me?

1068
01:05:29,342 --> 01:05:30,760
I'm so upset.

1069
01:05:32,637 --> 01:05:34,597
What kind of sad dream did you have?

1070
01:05:49,696 --> 01:05:50,572
Hey.

1071
01:05:52,449 --> 01:05:53,950
Did I wake you?

1072
01:05:55,702 --> 01:05:56,911
Sleep outside.

1073
01:05:58,788 --> 01:06:00,665
- Why?
- Go sleep on the couch.

1074
01:06:02,041 --> 01:06:03,293
The couch is a bit--

1075
01:06:03,376 --> 01:06:04,335
Leave now.

1076
01:06:05,670 --> 01:06:07,046
Go. Now.

1077
01:06:09,841 --> 01:06:10,800
Come on.

1078
01:06:12,343 --> 01:06:13,803
Close the door behind you.

1079
01:06:13,887 --> 01:06:15,138
You're so cold.

1080
01:06:19,976 --> 01:06:20,977
Fine.

1081
01:06:22,020 --> 01:06:22,937
Good night.

1082
01:06:33,615 --> 01:06:37,076
Why did you call
this emergency partner meeting?

1083
01:06:37,160 --> 01:06:39,329
And why did you explicitly ask

1084
01:06:39,412 --> 01:06:42,123
for a specific partner
to be excluded from this meeting?

1085
01:06:42,207 --> 01:06:43,416
Right.

1086
01:06:43,500 --> 01:06:45,752
That specific partner
I asked to be excluded

1087
01:06:45,835 --> 01:06:47,504
is the item on the agenda for the meeting.

1088
01:06:47,587 --> 01:06:49,672
Mr. Yoon Seok-hoon is the item?

1089
01:06:50,298 --> 01:06:51,466
Yes, that is correct.

1090
01:06:53,051 --> 01:06:54,260
Someone sent

1091
01:06:56,012 --> 01:06:59,474
this photo to my office anonymously.

1092
01:07:02,644 --> 01:07:03,895
Do you recognize them?

1093
01:07:05,063 --> 01:07:07,065
It's a photo of Ms. Seo Hye-jin

1094
01:07:07,148 --> 01:07:11,152
entering Mr. Yoon Seok-hoon's house
at a very late hour in the night.

1095
01:07:11,236 --> 01:07:12,487
Gosh.

1096
01:07:12,570 --> 01:07:14,614
We don't know what their relationship is

1097
01:07:14,697 --> 01:07:17,450
just based on a photo
of her entering his house.

1098
01:07:17,534 --> 01:07:20,370
And even if they're dating,
what's the problem?

1099
01:07:20,453 --> 01:07:23,122
He's breaking the very policy he created.

1100
01:07:23,206 --> 01:07:25,667
How hypocritical is that?

1101
01:07:28,878 --> 01:07:32,382
It feels a bit uncouth to discuss
Mr. Yoon's personal life like this,

1102
01:07:32,465 --> 01:07:35,093
but I believe he's divorced.
It wouldn't be an affair.

1103
01:07:35,176 --> 01:07:37,095
Must we go this far?

1104
01:07:37,178 --> 01:07:39,180
Mr. Yoon Seok-hoon

1105
01:07:39,264 --> 01:07:42,976
has compromised the ethical principles
and integrity of our organization.

1106
01:07:43,518 --> 01:07:44,852
What do you mean?

1107
01:07:44,936 --> 01:07:47,897
He entered an inappropriate relationship
with a junior lawyer

1108
01:07:47,981 --> 01:07:50,525
to manipulate her
into unscrupulously acquiring…

1109
01:07:52,610 --> 01:07:54,529
confidential documents
from the opposing party,

1110
01:07:54,612 --> 01:07:55,738
which he intended to exploit.

1111
01:07:55,822 --> 01:07:58,074
He has undermined
the ethical principles and integrity

1112
01:07:58,157 --> 01:08:00,285
of the ethical wall we have established

1113
01:08:00,368 --> 01:08:04,664
through years of building trust
and attempted to dismantle it.

1114
01:08:10,086 --> 01:08:11,671
What do you all think you're doing?

1115
01:09:07,894 --> 01:09:10,980
BEYOND THE BAR

1116
01:09:11,189 --> 01:09:13,107
Big news! This is insane.

1117
01:09:13,191 --> 01:09:14,275
- He resigned.
- What?

1118
01:09:14,359 --> 01:09:16,486
- I won't explain myself.
<i>- What a mess.</i>

1119
01:09:16,569 --> 01:09:18,112
<i>I even thought about ending my life.</i>

1120
01:09:18,196 --> 01:09:19,989
<i>But I came to you as a last resort.</i>

1121
01:09:20,073 --> 01:09:21,282
Seriously?

1122
01:09:21,366 --> 01:09:24,410
Tell me what's going on right now.

1123
01:09:24,494 --> 01:09:25,370
Seol-yeon!

1124
01:09:26,120 --> 01:09:28,539
<i>All the evidence was secured,</i>
<i>and she was arrested on the spot.</i>

1125
01:09:28,623 --> 01:09:29,499
<i>Something feels off.</i>

1126
01:09:29,582 --> 01:09:31,376
<i>I guess your next target is Kang Hyo-min.</i>

1127
01:09:31,459 --> 01:09:33,294
Start groveling
if you don't want to be buried.

1128
01:09:33,378 --> 01:09:36,881
<i>To me, justice means protecting</i>
<i>the people I have to protect.</i>

1129
01:09:36,964 --> 01:09:38,758
Even if it's something illegal?

1130
01:09:42,011 --> 01:09:44,013
